caption.title: Demographic history of the HIV-1 CRF03_AB recombinant in the former Soviet Union.
caption.p: Estimates of the effective population size (Ne) through time (t) using Bayesian Skyline (green) and Bayesian GMRF (violet) coalescent model are presented on a logarithmic scale as median (solid color line) with the corresponding 95% HPD credibility interval (color area).
